{"title":"Controls","content":"The controls interface is a modal sub-interface that can be opened through the settings interface.\n\nIt can be used to view and customize the keyboard keybinds that the player uses to control the game. At most two different keybinds can be defined for each customizable action. Controls can also be reset to their default state.\n\nCustomization of mouse buttons is going to be added soon.\n\nPlayers control the game with their mouse and keyboard. While the chat is open, a keybind can be used by pressing Ctrl + keybind.\n\nThe following keybinds work while controlling a player character.\n\nThe following keybinds take priority in combat.\n\nThe following mouse actions work while controlling a player character.\n\n\n\n","tables":[[{"Game action":{"text":"Toggle fullscreen"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"CTRL-F"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"❌"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Open chat"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"Tab"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"Return"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Sense spell"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"Space bar"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"❌"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Rotate camera up"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"Up arrow"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"W"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Rotate camera left"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"Left arrow"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"A"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Rotate camera down"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"Down arrow"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"S"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Rotate camera right"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"Right arrow"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"D"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Open map interface"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"M"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"❌"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Open quest interface"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"Q"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"❌"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Open professions interface"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"P"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"❌"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Open backpack interface"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"I"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"❌"}},{"Game action":{"text":"Open toolbelt interface"},"Keybind 1":{"text":"T"},"Keybind 2":{"text":"❌"}},{"Game action":{"text"